<h3 class="wp-block-heading wp-block-paragraph">4. Which technological solutions can be used to save energy in student houses?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Technological solutions such as smart thermostats, energy monitoring applications, solar energy systems, smart lighting systems and smart sockets can be used.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="5-how-can-i-track-my-energy-consumption">5. How can I track my energy consumption?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You can analyze your energy consumption by tracking your electricity bill and using energy monitoring apps.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-09-03T10:37:17Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:44:30Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/kling_20250807_Text_to_Image__A_cozy_st_5242_1-1.webp","alt":"Students saving energy together in a cozy shared apartment.","title":"kling_20250807_Text_to_Image__A_cozy_st_5242_1"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'energy-efficiency-in-student-homes' );
