<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="where-to-find-second-hand-books-and-course-notes-in-turkey">Where to Find Second Hand Books and Course Notes in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">There are many places and platforms where you can find second-hand books and lecture notes. These resources offer students the opportunity to save money and adopt an environmentally friendly approach. Here are some places in Turkey where you can find these resources:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Libraries:</strong> University libraries sometimes offer second-hand books. In addition, some libraries organize book exchange events.</li>



<li><strong>Bookstores:</strong> Local second-hand bookstores are a good source for finding textbooks and literary works.</li>



<li><strong>University Second-Hand Book Sale Events:</strong> Some universities organize events where students can sell unused books.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You can also take a look at <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/en/cargo-courier-services-costs-in-turkey/">Cargo and Courier Service Costs in Turkey</a>.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="popular-second-hand-book-and-note-sales-sites-in-turkey">Popular Second Hand Book and Course Notes Sales Sites in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Online platforms are one of the most practical ways to access second-hand books and lecture notes. Some popular second-hand book and note selling sites in Turkey are:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong><a href="http://www.letgo.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Letgo</a>:</strong> It is a platform where users can buy and sell second-hand products. It offers a wide selection in the book category.</li>



<li><strong><a href="https://www.nadirkitap.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Rare Book</a>:</strong> It is a preferred site especially for rare and second-hand books. You can also find textbooks and academic resources here.</li>



<li><strong><a href="https://www.sahibinden.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sahibinden</a>:</strong> is another widely used platform for second-hand books. Users can list their books here.</li>
</ul>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="lesson-note-sharing-groups-and-communities-what-they-offer">Course Notes Sharing Groups and Communities: What They Offer</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Lesson note sharing groups allow students to exchange information with each other. These groups are often found on social media platforms or forums. Here are some examples:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Facebook Groups:</strong> Groups such as the &#8220;University Lecture Notes Sharing Group&#8221; are places where students can share lecture notes and find the resources they need.</li>



<li><strong>WhatsApp and Telegram Groups:</strong> These platforms are used for faster communication and information sharing. Students can share lecture notes and resources instantly.</li>



<li><strong>Forums:</strong> Some university forums allow students to share lecture notes and resources.</li>
</ul>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="second-hand-book-shops-preferred-by-students">Second Hand Book Shops Preferred by Students</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Second-hand bookstores, which are often preferred by students, are usually located near university campuses. Here are some popular shops:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Campus Bookstore:</strong> Located on university campuses, these shops allow students to find the textbooks they need.</li>



<li><strong>Local Second-Hand Shops:</strong> Located in city centers or around universities, these shops offer a variety of books at affordable prices.</li>
</ul>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="second-hand-book-fairs-and-events-in-turkey">Second Hand Book Fairs and Events in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Book fairs and events in Turkey offer great opportunities to find second-hand books. Many publishers and vendors come together at such events. Here are some important events:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Istanbul Book Fair:</strong> Organized every year, this fair is attended by many publishing houses and second-hand book sellers.</li>



<li><strong>Ankara Book Fair:</strong> Held in Ankara, this fair offers students and book lovers a wide selection of second-hand books.</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="find-affordable-resources-and-start-learning-now">Where to find second-hand course notes?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Course notes can be found in social media groups, forums and university libraries.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-should-i-look-for-when-buying-a-used-book">What should I look for when buying a second-hand?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You should pay attention to the physical condition of the books, publisher information and price. It is also important to check the credibility of the seller.</p>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading">When are second-hand fairs held?</h3>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Second-hand book fairs are usually held at certain times of the year, especially in the fall and spring. You can follow the fairs in Istanbul and Ankara.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="why-second-hand-books-should-be-preferred">Why second-hand books should be preferred</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Second-hand books offer a more affordable option than new books and can help you develop a sustainable reading habit. They also offer the chance to find rare works.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">With this information, you can take the right steps to find second-hand books and lecture notes in Turkey. Don&#8217;t forget to make use of these resources throughout your studies!</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2026-01-19T11:09:18Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2026-03-15T18:39:32Z', "featured_image" = '{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/a-guide-to-finding-secondhand-books-and-lecture-notes-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"A man sitting at a desk browsing secondhand book websites on his laptop, with a bookshelf in the background.","title":"a-guide-to-finding-secondhand-books-and-lecture-notes-in-turkiye"}' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'finding-second-hand-book-lecture-notes';
