able services.","name":"Cargo and Courier Service Costs in Turkey","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/cargo-courier-services-costs-in-turkey/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/cargo-courier-services-costs-in-turkey/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/shipping-and-courier-service-costs-in-turkey.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/cargo-courier-services-costs-in-turkey/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey is a major hub for cargo and courier services, both nationally and internationally. Especially with the rise of e-commerce in recent years, the costs and variety of these services have increased dramatically. In this article, we will provide comprehensive information about cargo and courier services in Turkey, examine the factors affecting costs, and discuss the options available for international students.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="cargo-and-courier-options-in-turkey-for-international-students">Cargo and Courier Options in Turkey for International Students</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">International students can benefit from various cargo and courier services while studying in Turkey. Universities in Turkey offer a variety of services to meet the needs of students. For example:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Sending Educational Materials:</strong> International students can send their educational materials or books from their home countries to Turkey. In this process, fast and reliable cargo companies should be preferred.</li>



<li><strong>Sending Personal Belongings:</strong> Students may wish to send personal belongings while studying in Turkey. In this case, it is important to choose an affordable and reliable courier service.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Recommended cargo and courier companies include PTT, Yurtiçi Kargo, Aras Kargo and MNG Kargo. These companies also offer services for international shipments.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="factors-affecting-prices-in-cargo-and-courier-services">Factors Affecting Prices in Cargo and Courier Services</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The costs of cargo and courier services vary depending on several factors. Here are these factors:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Shipping Network:</strong> The size of the shipping company&#8217;s international and national network is an important factor affecting prices. Companies with a wider network can often offer more favorable rates.</li>



<li><strong>Shipment Weight and Size:</strong> The weight and size of the shipped package directly affects the costs. Generally, heavier and larger packages are charged more.</li>



<li><strong>Service Type:</strong> There are price differences between standard, express or economy service options. Express services for urgent shipments may be more expensive.</li>



<li><strong>Insurance and Extra Services:</strong> Additional options, such as insuring the shipment or tracking services, can increase the total cost.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You can also check out <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/en/car-rental-for-students-in-turkey/">Car Rental Options for Students in Turkey</a>.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-is-the-general-cost-of-cargo-and-courier-services-in-turkey">What is the General Cost of Cargo and Courier Services in Turkey?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The costs of cargo and courier services in Turkey vary depending on the factors mentioned above. In general, the prices for international shipments are as follows:</p>


<table style="background-color: var(--base-3);color: var(--contrast)">
<thead>
<tr>
<th><strong>Package Type</strong></th>
<th><strong>Weight Range</strong></th>
<th><strong>Average Fee (USD)</strong></th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Small Package</td>
<td>1-5 kg</td>
<td>$10 &#8211; $25</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Medium Size Package</td>
<td>5-10 kg</td>
<td>$25 &#8211; $50</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Big Package</td>
<td>10 kg and over</td>
<td>$50 and up</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">These prices may vary depending on the selected shipping company and type of service. Especially during campaign periods, some cargo companies may offer discounts.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="which-companies-stand-out-in-cargo-and-courier-services-in-turkey">Which Companies Stand Out in Cargo and Courier Services in Turkey?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">There are many companies offering cargo and courier services in Turkey. However, some stand out for their experience in the sector and customer satisfaction. Here are some of these companies:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong><a href="https://www.yurticikargo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PTT</a>:</strong> PTT, Turkey&#8217;s national postal service, offers affordable rates for both national and international shipments.</li>



<li><strong><a href="https://www.yurticikargo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yurtici Cargo:</a></strong> Yurtiçi Kargo, which has a wide distribution network, is known for its fast and reliable services.</li>



<li><strong><a href="https://www.araskargo.com.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Aras Cargo</a>:</strong> Offering fast service especially in local shipments, Aras Kargo attaches importance to customer satisfaction.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You can find the best option for your needs by getting price quotes from the websites of these companies.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-to-consider-when-shipping-abroad">What to Consider When Shipping Abroad</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">There are some important points to be considered when shipping abroad. Here are these points:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Customs Regulations:</strong> Each country has its own customs regulations. Before shipping, it is important to check the customs rules of the receiving country.</li>



<li><strong>Packaging:</strong> Secure packaging of shipped goods reduces the risk of damage. It is recommended to use special packaging materials, especially for fragile items.</li>



<li><strong>Shipment Tracking:</strong> To track the whereabouts of your shipment, remember to get the tracking number. This will keep you informed about the status of your shipment.</li>



<li><strong>Insurance:</strong> If you are sending valuable items, consider taking out insurance. This allows you to take a precaution against possible losses.</li>
</ul>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="discover-the-most-favorable-shipping-prices-now-take-advantage">Discover the most favorable shipping prices now, take advantage!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey is a country that offers a wide range of cargo and courier services. It is possible to find affordable and reliable services for international students. By considering the factors that affect costs, you can choose the most suitable shipping company for your needs. With the information we have provided in this article, you can make more informed decisions about cargo and courier services in Turkey. Remember, every shipping process can be made easier with the right planning and knowledge.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="frequently-asked-questions">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading">How long are the shipping times?</h3>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Cargo delivery times vary depending on the type of service selected and the distance. Standard shipments usually arrive within 3-7 business days, while express shipments arrive within 1-3 business days.</p>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Are there additional fees when shipping abroad?</h3>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Yes, there may be additional fees such as customs duties and insurance. It is important to research these additional costs before shipping.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-should-i-choose-between-shipping-companies">How should I choose between shipping companies?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">When choosing a shipping company, you should consider price, service quality, customer reviews and shipping times.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">How much does shipping cost to Turkey?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Shipping a 20 kg parcel to Turkey varies by origin. From <strong>Europe (e.g., Germany)</strong>, it costs approximately <strong>€30–€50</strong> via DHL. From the <strong>UK</strong>, expect to pay around <strong>£50–£80</strong> using economy services like Parcelforce. From the <strong>USA</strong>, rates are significantly higher, often exceeding <strong>$150–$250</strong> with carriers like FedEx or UPS.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What is the cost of air cargo per kg?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Air cargo rates for larger commercial shipments (freight) generally range from <strong>$3.00 to $7.00 USD per kg</strong>. For example, importing from China to Turkey averages <strong>$4.50–$7.00/kg</strong>, while exporting from Turkey to Europe (like Germany or UK) is often cheaper, around <strong>€1.10–€2.00/kg</strong> for shipments over 100 kg.</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2026-01-18T09:28:00Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2026-03-15T18:39:35Z', "featured_image" = '{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/shipping-and-courier-service-costs-in-turkey.webp","alt":"A delivery truck and courier handing over a package in a Turkish city street.","title":"shipping-and-courier-service-costs-in-turkey"}' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'cargo-courier-services-costs-in-turkey';
